cs.NI, cs.CY, cs.CR, cs.IT, cs.SY 

The paper focuses on the integration of digital technology into transportation infrastructure to support connected vehicle applications. This falls under the category of computer networks (cs.NI) as it involves communication between vehicles and infrastructure. Additionally, the paper discusses the importance of cybersecurity (cs.CY) in ensuring the reliability and security of data transmission. The paper also touches on the collection and processing of data, which falls under the category of cryptography and security (cs.CR) and information theory (cs.IT). Finally, the paper emphasizes the need for collaboration and coordination in the planning and deployment of digital infrastructure, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY).
